le":52,"path":53,"stem":54},"Am5000","/machines/cable-and-wire-processing-machines/am5000","machines/cable-and-wire-processing-machines/4.am5000",{"title":56,"path":57,"stem":58},"Triathlon 3000 Triathlon 3000plus","/machines/cable-and-wire-processing-machines/triathlon-3000-triathlon-3000plus","machines/cable-and-wire-processing-machines/5.triathlon-3000-triathlon-3000plus",{"title":60,"path":61,"stem":62,"children":63,"icon":33},"Corrugated Conduit","/machines/corrugated-conduit","machines/3.corrugated-conduit",[64,68],{"title":65,"path":66,"stem":67},"Ct4100 Ct4200","/machines/corrugated-conduit/ct4100-ct4200","machines/corrugated-conduit/1.ct4100-ct4200",{"title":69,"path":70,"stem":71},"Sm4000","/machines/corrugated-conduit/sm4000","machines/corrugated-conduit/2.sm4000",{"title":73,"path":74,"stem":75,"icon":33},"Spare Parts and Service","/machines/spare-parts-and-service","machines/4.spare-parts-and-service",{"page":77,"surround":102},{"id":78,"title":79,"body":80,"description":97,"extension":98,"meta":99,"navigation":100,"path":11,"seo":101,"stem":12},"machines/machines/profile-plastic-rubber-cutting-machines/1.st-ob.md","Metzner ST-OB",{"type":81,"value":82,"toc":93},"minimal",[83,87,90],[84,85,86],"p",{},"The ST-OB is a very well established and extremely robust machine which is versatile in its ability to cut tubes, textiles and extruded profiles to length with high accuracy. Used in a variety of industries from automotive door seals to hoses in the medical industry.",[84,88,89],{},"The machine can be supplied with three interchangeable cutting mechanisms for die cut (kiss cut), tube cut or shear cut. These cutting heads make the ST0OB a very versatile machine with multiple applications.",[84,91,92],{},"Material is pulled into the machine via two feed belts (top and bottom) and these are tensioned by hand to give a good grip without excessive pressure. The pneumatic cylinder, which operated the cutting blade, is specially developed for Metzner, it gives high power for cutting but also vents quickly for a quick cutting speed.",{"title":94,"searchDepth":95,"depth":95,"links":96},"",2,[],"The ST-OB is a very well established and extremely robust machine.","md",{},{"title":10},{"title":79,"description":97},[103,105],{"title":5,"path":6,"stem":7,"children":-1,"description":104,"icon":33},"Metzner produce a wide range of machines capable of cutting many different rubber and plastic extrusions.",{"title":14,"path":15,"stem":16,"description":106,"children":-1},"The Variocut is a very versatile cutting machine with a range of exchangeable cutting mechanisms which allows for accurate cut to length of a variety of materials including tubes, hoses, extrusions, pipes, foils, cables and wires.",1738275439757]